<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c1">" فيه ضعف"</span>. <span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(٧/ ٢٩١)</span>. <span class="c1">"أحد الضعفاء"</span>. <span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(٤/ ٢٨٧)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
